1
00:02:12,850 --> 00:02:15,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Episode 10</font>

2
00:02:18,000 --> 00:02:20,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Agree to my three conditions,</font>

3
00:02:20,200 --> 00:02:22,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and you can leave.</font>

4
00:02:24,410 --> 00:02:26,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you believe me?</font>

5
00:02:26,220 --> 00:02:28,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It really wasn't me!</font>

6
00:02:28,020 --> 00:02:29,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Believe you?</font>

7
00:02:29,730 --> 00:02:31,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How can I believe you?</font>

8
00:02:31,380 --> 00:02:34,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even those who have awakened the 
Bright Soul Skill can't handle you.</font>

9
00:02:35,290 --> 00:02:38,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I've watched you kids grow up.</font>

10
00:02:38,530 --> 00:02:41,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know exactly what kind
of person you are.</font>

11
00:02:42,160 --> 00:02:43,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't do it!</font>

12
00:02:44,660 --> 00:02:46,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then prove it to me!</font>

13
00:02:46,990 --> 00:02:49,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not like I didn't give you a chance.</font>

14
00:02:49,250 --> 00:02:51,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When you were first caught by the clan,</font>

15
00:02:51,630 --> 00:02:54,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">if some people hadn't turned a blind eye,</font>

16
00:02:54,030 --> 00:02:57,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">do you think you could've escaped 
the village on your own?</font>

17
00:02:57,190 --> 00:02:59,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But after you fled,</font>

18
00:02:59,360 --> 00:03:02,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">did you go looking
for Huan's actual killer?</font>

19
00:03:09,500 --> 00:03:10,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, you didn't.</font>

20
00:03:11,430 --> 00:03:15,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You ran off and had fun hanging out 
with those Quan Xing brats!</font>

21
00:03:16,380 --> 00:03:19,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I... I really had nowhere 
else to go at the time.</font>

22
00:03:19,670 --> 00:03:20,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bullshit!</font>

23
00:03:20,810 --> 00:03:25,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You mean righteous clans feared
our Lyu Clan and wouldn't take you in.</font>

24
00:03:25,600 --> 00:03:27,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let me name three people!</font>

25
00:03:27,700 --> 00:03:29,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Zhang Zhiwei of the Tenshifu.</font>

26
00:03:29,320 --> 00:03:32,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't compare to him in terms of 
character, strength, or influence.</font>

27
00:03:32,520 --> 00:03:34,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mu You of Xiaozhan.</font>

28
00:03:34,040 --> 00:03:36,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The most upstanding of 
the younger generation!</font>

29
00:03:36,600 --> 00:03:39,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And Lu Jin, head of the Lu Clan.</font>

30
00:03:39,390 --> 00:03:41,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't get along with him.</font>

31
00:03:41,120 --> 00:03:43,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I won't deny he's a good man!</font>

32
00:03:43,770 --> 00:03:46,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just hate that he's too clean!</font>

33
00:03:46,350 --> 00:03:49,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've never seen eye to eye,
 even since childhood.</font>

34
00:03:49,520 --> 00:03:50,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you were truly wronged,</font>

35
00:03:50,860 --> 00:03:52,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you could've gone to any one of them!</font>

36
00:03:52,900 --> 00:03:56,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All three know I'm ruthless, 
but none of them fear me!</font>

37
00:03:56,100 --> 00:04:01,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They wouldn't just listen to the
village's story and hand you back!</font>

38
00:04:01,470 --> 00:04:05,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And they all have the ability to 
help you track down the real killer!</font>

39
00:04:05,390 --> 00:04:09,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you really were innocent, 
those three were your best options!</font>

40
00:04:09,250 --> 00:04:11,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you...</font>

41
00:04:11,060 --> 00:04:15,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You chose the lowest of the 
low, the Quan Xing Sect!</font>

42
00:04:15,970 --> 00:04:19,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't even explain
why yourself, can you?</font>

43
00:04:19,830 --> 00:04:21,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let me tell you...</font>

44
00:04:21,590 --> 00:04:23,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Birds of a feather flock together!</font>

45
00:04:23,930 --> 00:04:27,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Compared to staying in the 
village and following my rules,</font>

46
00:04:27,100 --> 00:04:31,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it's much more fun to mess around 
with those freaks, right?</font>

47
00:04:32,090 --> 00:04:34,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even setting aside Huan's matter,</font>

48
00:04:34,460 --> 00:04:36,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the beatings you've taken these days...</font>

49
00:04:36,800 --> 00:04:38,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Were they unfair?</font>

50
00:04:39,120 --> 00:04:40,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not unfair.</font>

51
00:04:40,270 --> 00:04:43,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right, three conditions!</font>

52
00:04:43,750 --> 00:04:47,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">First, from now on, cut all 
ties with the Quan Xing Sect!</font>

53
00:04:47,750 --> 00:04:49,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No more contact!</font>

54
00:04:49,810 --> 00:04:53,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Second, from now on, you will 
follow me and learn Ruyi Jin.</font>

55
00:04:55,910 --> 00:04:57,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Me?</font>

56
00:04:58,600 --> 00:05:00,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How could I possibly learn it?</font>

57
00:05:00,350 --> 00:05:01,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Grandfather tried to teach me.</font>

58
00:05:02,100 --> 00:05:06,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mastering innate and acquired abilities 
simultaneously is extremely difficult,</font>

59
00:05:06,430 --> 00:05:08,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but not impossible!</font>

60
00:05:08,650 --> 00:05:11,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And didn't you hear what I just said?</font>

61
00:05:11,570 --> 00:05:13,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">From now on, you'll follow me!</font>

62
00:05:13,400 --> 00:05:14,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll train you personally!</font>

63
00:05:16,220 --> 00:05:17,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One last condition.</font>

64
00:05:17,640 --> 00:05:20,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After you recover, prepare 
to marry Qi from Dongcun.</font>

65
00:05:21,460 --> 00:05:24,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Qi? You mean Lyu Qi?</font>

66
00:05:24,340 --> 00:05:25,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How can that be...</font>

67
00:05:25,560 --> 00:05:29,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not satisfied? You don't like 
her looks or personality?</font>

68
00:05:30,540 --> 00:05:33,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh yeah, her Ruyi Jin is really advanced.</font>

69
00:05:33,190 --> 00:05:34,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Afraid of getting beaten up later?</font>

70
00:05:34,830 --> 00:05:38,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, she's a relative from 
within five generations!</font>

71
00:05:38,220 --> 00:05:40,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So what?</font>

72
00:05:40,000 --> 00:05:43,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Back then, your Great-Uncle, 
Grandfather, and Third Great-Aunt</font>

73
00:05:43,360 --> 00:05:45,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">all married within their own clan.</font>

74
00:05:46,600 --> 00:05:48,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">B-But...</font>

75
00:05:49,020 --> 00:05:50,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you refuse?</font>

76
00:05:51,140 --> 00:05:54,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I... Great-Grandfather...</font>

77
00:05:55,330 --> 00:05:57,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huan's matter hasn't been...</font>

78
00:05:58,460 --> 00:06:01,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why... Why are you doing this for me?</font>

79
00:06:02,210 --> 00:06:04,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why am I treating you so well?</font>

80
00:06:06,850 --> 00:06:09,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course Huan's matter isn't over.</font>

81
00:06:09,440 --> 00:06:11,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I ever find out it really was you,</font>

82
00:06:11,580 --> 00:06:13,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll kill you with my own hands.</font>

83
00:06:13,730 --> 00:06:15,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If it wasn't you,</font>

84
00:06:15,600 --> 00:06:18,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">then you go and investigate!</font>

85
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:20,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You think just because I'm letting you go,</font>

86
00:06:20,500 --> 00:06:23,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you can escape my grasp?</font>

87
00:06:27,070 --> 00:06:28,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lyu Liang,</font>

88
00:06:29,230 --> 00:06:31,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">deep down, I hope it wasn't you.</font>

89
00:06:32,560 --> 00:06:35,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You all think I'm ruthless, 
that I'm heartless.</font>

90
00:06:36,820 --> 00:06:38,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I do think I'm pretty harsh myself.</font>

91
00:06:39,170 --> 00:06:41,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you also need to understand,</font>

92
00:06:41,190 --> 00:06:44,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the only thing that truly 
matters to me is bloodline.</font>

93
00:06:44,140 --> 00:06:46,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even a ridiculous guy like you,</font>

94
00:06:46,920 --> 00:06:48,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I cherish you in my own way.</font>

95
00:06:49,900 --> 00:06:51,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Great-Grandfather...</font>

96
00:06:52,270 --> 00:06:53,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, right, Great-Grandfather...</font>

97
00:06:53,920 --> 00:06:56,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's something I wanted to ask you.</font>

98
00:06:56,890 --> 00:06:59,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you know what "Perfect Hands" is?</font>

99
00:07:11,370 --> 00:07:14,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where did you hear that name?</font>

100
00:07:19,310 --> 00:07:21,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait...</font>

101
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:26,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry, I won't hurt you.</font>

102
00:07:26,680 --> 00:07:27,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll be fine.</font>

103
00:07:28,200 --> 00:07:32,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That technique you used on 
me just now... that was...</font>

104
00:07:35,030 --> 00:07:36,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is your memory.</font>

105
00:07:36,630 --> 00:07:39,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A technique passed down in our 
Lyu Clan, the Bright Soul Skill.</font>

106
00:07:41,270 --> 00:07:43,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's specifically designed 
to deal with this place.</font>

107
00:07:44,300 --> 00:07:46,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bright Soul Skill...</font>

108
00:07:46,660 --> 00:07:48,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bright Soul Skill...</font>

109
00:07:50,730 --> 00:07:53,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have no idea what you're doing.</font>

110
00:07:55,800 --> 00:07:59,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Child, let me give you 
one more piece of advice.</font>

111
00:07:59,430 --> 00:08:02,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Leave the Quan Xing Sect
as soon as possible.</font>

112
00:08:02,460 --> 00:08:03,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

113
00:08:03,560 --> 00:08:08,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If they'll make things difficult
for Zhang Chulan over Qi Genesis,</font>

114
00:08:08,550 --> 00:08:11,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">then you're not safe with them either.</font>

115
00:08:12,140 --> 00:08:14,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What... do you mean?</font>

116
00:08:15,290 --> 00:08:18,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've seen your technique before,
 a long time ago.</font>

117
00:08:18,960 --> 00:08:21,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was exactly the same.</font>

118
00:08:21,040 --> 00:08:25,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But back then, it wasn't 
called "Bright Soul Skill,"</font>

119
00:08:25,350 --> 00:08:28,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but "Perfect Hands."</font>

120
00:08:31,300 --> 00:08:35,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's... one of the Eight Secret 
Arts from the Jiashen year.</font>

121
00:08:35,560 --> 00:08:39,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why would Tian Jinzhong say that?</font>

122
00:08:44,960 --> 00:08:45,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Great-Grandfather!</font>

123
00:08:46,640 --> 00:08:48,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You wait here.</font>

124
00:08:49,350 --> 00:08:50,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Great-Grandfather.</font>

125
00:08:58,890 --> 00:09:00,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Father!</font>

126
00:09:00,370 --> 00:09:02,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Father... how did it go?</font>

127
00:09:02,180 --> 00:09:03,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lyu Liang, he...</font>

128
00:09:07,310 --> 00:09:11,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lyu Zhong, go and take 
what's in Lyu Liang's head.</font>

129
00:09:15,060 --> 00:09:15,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Father?</font>

130
00:09:18,180 --> 00:09:21,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go get the village doctor.</font>

131
00:09:37,180 --> 00:09:39,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Great-Grandfather! Great-</font>

132
00:09:49,680 --> 00:09:50,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come in!</font>

133
00:10:14,210 --> 00:10:16,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want him alive.</font>

134
00:10:16,520 --> 00:10:20,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Every drop of our clan's blood
 is precious.</font>

135
00:10:27,360 --> 00:10:29,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">President Qu, this way please.</font>

136
00:10:40,550 --> 00:10:44,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yaoxing Society, Qu Tong? 
I've heard a lot about you.</font>

137
00:10:44,600 --> 00:10:46,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. Mu You of Xiaozhan.</font>

138
00:10:47,360 --> 00:10:49,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Chairman Zhao, what's this about?</font>

139
00:10:50,410 --> 00:10:51,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not much.</font>

140
00:10:51,850 --> 00:10:54,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just need both your teams 
to help out with something.</font>

141
00:11:01,030 --> 00:11:04,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This shows the location of one 
of the Company's secret bunkers.</font>

142
00:11:09,770 --> 00:11:11,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How did it come to this?</font>

143
00:11:12,320 --> 00:11:14,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why didn't you tell me beforehand...?</font>

144
00:11:14,400 --> 00:11:16,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just got the news myself!</font>

145
00:11:16,330 --> 00:11:20,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Zhao Fangxu didn't discuss this 
with the Board before taking action.</font>

146
00:11:20,530 --> 00:11:23,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He planned to act first and report 
later from the very start.</font>

147
00:11:23,900 --> 00:11:27,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As things stand, even if he 
notified the Board afterwards,</font>

148
00:11:27,250 --> 00:11:29,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">they wouldn't refuse him.</font>

149
00:11:29,670 --> 00:11:32,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's already starting to
suspect the Board.</font>

150
00:11:32,540 --> 00:11:33,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So what?</font>

151
00:11:33,920 --> 00:11:36,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No one will fall for such a stupid plan!</font>

152
00:11:37,270 --> 00:11:38,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not necessarily.</font>

153
00:11:38,680 --> 00:11:41,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This time it might
actually be troublesome.</font>

154
00:11:41,640 --> 00:11:43,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't refuse Zhao Fangxu.</font>

155
00:11:43,740 --> 00:11:45,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I do, they'll suspect me.</font>

156
00:11:46,160 --> 00:11:48,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Company really got lucky this time.</font>

157
00:11:52,270 --> 00:11:53,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Zhang Lingyu</font>

158
00:11:53,020 --> 00:11:56,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}If it's convenient, I'll come over now...</font>

159
00:11:57,200 --> 00:11:58,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bao'er.</font>

160
00:11:59,850 --> 00:12:01,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You wouldn't mind an
extra roommate, right?</font>

161
00:12:06,470 --> 00:12:09,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The number you dialed is 
temporarily unavailable.</i></font>

162
00:12:14,390 --> 00:12:19,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Big Wang</font>

163
00:12:14,780 --> 00:12:15,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This guy...</font>

164
00:12:16,510 --> 00:12:19,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I haven't been able to reach him ever
since we parted ways at Biyou Village.</font>

165
00:12:21,000 --> 00:12:21,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welcome!</font>

166
00:12:22,150 --> 00:12:23,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A very warm welcome!</font>

167
00:12:23,280 --> 00:12:26,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">On behalf of the Company, I offer 
Master Lingyu a very warm welcome!</font>

168
00:12:28,890 --> 00:12:31,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I... have one more condition.</font>

169
00:12:31,440 --> 00:12:31,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Name it.</font>

170
00:12:33,600 --> 00:12:34,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can I not cut my hair?</font>

171
00:12:34,990 --> 00:12:37,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I understand there are regulations, but...</font>

172
00:12:39,100 --> 00:12:40,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that okay?</font>

173
00:12:43,610 --> 00:12:45,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master Lingyu, you're overthinking it!</font>

174
00:12:45,870 --> 00:12:47,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come, let's get you settled first.</font>

175
00:12:47,680 --> 00:12:49,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's an empty room downstairs.</font>

176
00:12:49,520 --> 00:12:51,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can tidy it up yourself.</font>

177
00:12:51,180 --> 00:12:54,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Living in the same building as a girl?</font>

178
00:12:54,090 --> 00:12:55,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's inconvenient.</font>

179
00:12:56,640 --> 00:12:58,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's inconvenient about it?</font>

180
00:12:58,390 --> 00:13:01,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I never expected Master Lingyu to take 
gender distinctions so seriously.</font>

181
00:13:03,610 --> 00:13:04,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Brother Si!</font>

182
00:13:04,200 --> 00:13:04,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah?</font>

183
00:13:05,970 --> 00:13:08,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come now, Master Lingyu, this way...</font>

184
00:13:12,880 --> 00:13:14,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now that Zhang Lingyu's sorted,</font>

185
00:13:14,580 --> 00:13:16,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">what about Lu Linglong and Lu Lin?</font>

186
00:13:16,220 --> 00:13:17,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're in Tianjin.</font>

187
00:13:18,300 --> 00:13:20,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lately, when you go out, 
have you noticed you're being watched?</font>

188
00:13:21,230 --> 00:13:22,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

189
00:13:26,800 --> 00:13:28,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're from Xiaozhan.</font>

190
00:13:28,640 --> 00:13:30,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those two rookies hired them.</font>

191
00:13:30,640 --> 00:13:34,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Xiaozhan's one of the largest intelligence
organizations in the Outcast world.</font>

192
00:13:34,330 --> 00:13:36,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How could they not maintain a good 
relationship with the Company?</font>

193
00:13:36,870 --> 00:13:38,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those two didn't even figure that out.</font>

194
00:13:38,930 --> 00:13:42,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The moment Xiaozhan received the request, 
they notified me immediately.</font>

195
00:13:42,490 --> 00:13:43,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What should we do?</font>

196
00:13:43,390 --> 00:13:45,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Should we drag them out and confront them?</font>

197
00:13:48,460 --> 00:13:50,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No need.
If they really got involved in this,</font>

198
00:13:51,600 --> 00:13:53,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">they deserve whatever happens.</font>

199
00:14:03,010 --> 00:14:04,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master!</font>

200
00:14:04,570 --> 00:14:06,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The thought of you being in danger</font>

201
00:14:06,730 --> 00:14:08,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">while I remained on the 
mountain doing nothing...</font>

202
00:14:09,600 --> 00:14:11,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I simply couldn't bear it!</font>

203
00:14:12,460 --> 00:14:13,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master!</font>

204
00:14:14,240 --> 00:14:16,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please forgive me this once.</font>

205
00:14:19,200 --> 00:14:22,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huanjin, did you hear what he said?</font>

206
00:14:22,600 --> 00:14:25,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So he came down the mountain for my sake.</font>

207
00:14:34,560 --> 00:14:37,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master, Lingyu has suffered 
enough humiliation.</font>

208
00:14:39,620 --> 00:14:42,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not laughing at Zhang Lingyu.</font>

209
00:14:42,180 --> 00:14:45,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm happy for Zhang Huaiyi.</font>

210
00:14:45,570 --> 00:14:47,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This Master Uncle of yours,</font>

211
00:14:47,570 --> 00:14:52,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">he seemed so calm and 
detached from the world.</font>

212
00:14:52,360 --> 00:14:57,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it wasn't until he teamed 
up with Master to fool me</font>

213
00:14:57,600 --> 00:15:01,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that I realized just how strong he was.</font>

214
00:15:02,720 --> 00:15:06,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Throughout my life as a cultivator,</font>

215
00:15:06,430 --> 00:15:09,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I always believed I surpassed 
him in every way.</font>

216
00:15:10,030 --> 00:15:12,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But today I've realized that</font>

217
00:15:12,370 --> 00:15:15,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">in terms of successors, I've lost.</font>

218
00:15:15,520 --> 00:15:19,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look at Zhang Chulan,
the one he left behind.</font>

219
00:15:20,590 --> 00:15:23,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right, Zhang Lingyu.</font>

220
00:15:23,290 --> 00:15:27,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">From now on, you are no longer 
a disciple of the Tenshifu.</font>

221
00:15:28,660 --> 00:15:31,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am no longer your master.</font>

222
00:16:00,360 --> 00:16:06,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They say the girls of
Youzhou are so fine...</font>

223
00:16:12,240 --> 00:16:14,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Miss Bao, what are you...</font>

224
00:16:15,850 --> 00:16:16,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">San's car.</font>

225
00:16:16,970 --> 00:16:18,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It needs maintenance.</font>

226
00:16:18,080 --> 00:16:19,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The suspension's a bit loose.</font>

227
00:16:20,000 --> 00:16:21,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can fix cars?</font>

228
00:16:21,650 --> 00:16:23,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's amazing...</font>

229
00:16:23,000 --> 00:16:24,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, it's not hard.</font>

230
00:16:24,870 --> 00:16:28,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fuel lines, circuits, pneumatics, 
moving parts. That's all.</font>

231
00:16:28,720 --> 00:16:30,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Impressive. Really impressive.</font>

232
00:16:31,690 --> 00:16:34,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really? Lots of people can do it.</font>

233
00:16:37,650 --> 00:16:38,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All done.</font>

234
00:16:43,720 --> 00:16:44,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eat?</font>

235
00:16:46,200 --> 00:16:47,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

236
00:17:09,330 --> 00:17:12,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Miss Bao, how long have 
you been with the Company?</font>

237
00:17:19,750 --> 00:17:21,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Many years.</i></font>

238
00:17:21,270 --> 00:17:22,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Many years...</i></font>

239
00:17:24,080 --> 00:17:26,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That makes you sound so old.</i></font>

240
00:17:26,160 --> 00:17:27,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What do you do at the Company?</i></font>

241
00:17:27,840 --> 00:17:31,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Whatever San, Si, or 
Zhang Chulan tell me to do.</i></font>

242
00:17:29,430 --> 00:17:31,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Chulan, what do you think?</font>

243
00:17:32,020 --> 00:17:33,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Chulan?</font>

244
00:17:34,390 --> 00:17:35,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's good!</font>

245
00:17:35,420 --> 00:17:37,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll follow your arrangements,
Chairman Zhao.</font>

246
00:17:38,160 --> 00:17:40,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um... what about that person?</font>

247
00:17:43,000 --> 00:17:45,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master Uncle, how are you 
getting along with Bao'er?</font>

248
00:17:47,340 --> 00:17:49,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Zhang Chulan, come here.</font>

249
00:17:49,920 --> 00:17:51,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">From Miss Bao's description,</font>

250
00:17:51,810 --> 00:17:53,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the Company seems a bit...</font>

251
00:17:53,860 --> 00:17:56,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even if I, Zhang Lingyu,
fall on hard times,</font>

252
00:17:56,030 --> 00:17:58,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I would never do anything 
against my conscience!</font>

253
00:17:58,560 --> 00:18:00,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's special! Her job is special.</font>

254
00:18:01,090 --> 00:18:02,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How could the Company act recklessly?</font>

255
00:18:02,520 --> 00:18:05,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you don't trust the Company, 
you should at least trust me!</font>

256
00:18:05,430 --> 00:18:06,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I disagree on that point.</font>

257
00:18:07,020 --> 00:18:09,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then you should at least 
trust your own conscience.</font>

258
00:18:09,920 --> 00:18:13,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">From now on, you'll have to 
experience everything for yourself.</font>

259
00:18:13,090 --> 00:18:14,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No one can tell you what to do.</font>

260
00:18:14,810 --> 00:18:17,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All I can say is, in order to survive,</font>

261
00:18:17,380 --> 00:18:21,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't mind ambiguous situations
and doing things I'd rather not.</font>

262
00:18:21,910 --> 00:18:23,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But if it crosses my boundaries,</font>

263
00:18:24,610 --> 00:18:26,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">then screw it all.</font>

264
00:18:27,940 --> 00:18:31,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master Uncle, I believe 
you also have boundaries.</font>

265
00:18:31,710 --> 00:18:33,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh right, you've got a job.</font>

266
00:18:34,050 --> 00:18:37,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your first job is to protect me.</font>

267
00:18:37,770 --> 00:18:39,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How about that?</font>

268
00:18:39,180 --> 00:18:41,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doesn't violate your conscience, right?</font>

269
00:18:49,640 --> 00:18:53,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Excellent, Mr. Xiaoxiao. 
Your breathing technique is excellent.</font>

270
00:18:53,660 --> 00:18:56,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've been very helpful. Thanks.</font>

271
00:18:56,460 --> 00:18:59,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's nothing. President 
Qu did me a big favor.</font>

272
00:18:59,770 --> 00:19:01,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whatever the request is,</font>

273
00:19:01,240 --> 00:19:03,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">as long as she asks,</font>

274
00:19:03,120 --> 00:19:04,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll do it.</font>

275
00:19:04,600 --> 00:19:05,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right.</font>

276
00:19:05,830 --> 00:19:09,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Almost everyone here has been 
helped by Sister at some point.</font>

277
00:19:09,680 --> 00:19:12,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is probably why no
one can refuse her.</font>

278
00:19:12,570 --> 00:19:14,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's the source of her magic.</font>

279
00:19:16,310 --> 00:19:20,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This furnace was forged by Sister 
using my Divine Craftsmanship,</font>

280
00:19:20,180 --> 00:19:21,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">combined with her own methods,</font>

281
00:19:21,870 --> 00:19:24,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to restore my missing memories.</font>

282
00:19:24,520 --> 00:19:27,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I want to use it to help more people.</font>

283
00:19:27,680 --> 00:19:29,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to become someone like Sister.</font>

284
00:19:31,060 --> 00:19:32,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You are you.</font>

285
00:19:32,440 --> 00:19:34,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why would you want to become me?</font>

286
00:19:36,720 --> 00:19:38,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sister, you're back!</font>

287
00:19:38,270 --> 00:19:40,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Xiaoxiao, please step out for a moment.</font>

288
00:19:49,050 --> 00:19:51,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Again, Sister?</font>

289
00:19:51,160 --> 00:19:53,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I haven't needed to take this for ages.</font>

290
00:19:53,220 --> 00:19:55,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take it. Be good.</font>

291
00:19:55,920 --> 00:20:00,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sister, back then you said it was because 
my mental state was unstable...</font>

292
00:20:00,020 --> 00:20:01,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take it!</font>

293
00:20:01,180 --> 00:20:03,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But now I don't feel like my mind is...</font>

294
00:20:03,670 --> 00:20:05,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take it!</font>

295
00:21:03,840 --> 00:21:05,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello, Chairman Zhao?</font>

296
00:21:06,400 --> 00:21:08,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let me know when you're ready.</font>

297
00:21:08,370 --> 00:21:10,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The draft can be sent out at any time.</font>

298
00:21:12,410 --> 00:21:14,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why not finish the job?</font>

299
00:21:14,640 --> 00:21:17,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just remove all his 
memories of Biyou Village!</font>

300
00:21:17,710 --> 00:21:20,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you think his trust in 
you is starting to waver,</font>

301
00:21:20,530 --> 00:21:21,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">then embed it deeper!</font>

302
00:21:21,660 --> 00:21:25,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A sound mind can repair itself,</font>

303
00:21:25,140 --> 00:21:26,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">as you very well know.</font>

304
00:21:26,990 --> 00:21:28,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After repeated repairs,</font>

305
00:21:28,430 --> 00:21:31,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">his mind has already become 
extremely unstable.</font>

306
00:21:31,470 --> 00:21:36,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If we continue, I'm worried about 
unpredictable consequences.</font>

307
00:21:36,180 --> 00:21:37,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So what?</font>

308
00:21:38,190 --> 00:21:40,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If he becomes useless, get rid of him!</font>

309
00:21:41,120 --> 00:21:47,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh? Since when have you been 
able to speak to me like this?</font>

310
00:21:47,060 --> 00:21:48,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah! No!</font>

311
00:21:48,320 --> 00:21:50,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I was just too concerned about you!</font>

312
00:21:51,890 --> 00:21:53,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've already given him the drugs.</font>

313
00:21:53,720 --> 00:21:56,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Unless someone wakes him up, 
he'll sleep for at least a week.</font>

314
00:21:56,930 --> 00:21:58,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As long as you have a plan.</font>

315
00:21:59,020 --> 00:22:00,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let me make this clear to you.</font>

316
00:22:00,750 --> 00:22:03,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's those few guys making a move again.</font>

317
00:22:03,020 --> 00:22:04,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You must be careful.</font>

318
00:22:07,330 --> 00:22:08,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hang up.</font>

319
00:22:11,350 --> 00:22:15,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Guys, do you really think this will work?</font>

320
00:22:15,010 --> 00:22:17,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I gave up a cushy job
to come here, you know!</font>

